The paper proposes a privacy-enhanced matrix factorization recommender system, which falls under the category of privacy-preserving data mining and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, the paper deals with data management and privacy concerns, which are relevant to the sub-categories of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.DB (Databases).
